---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="永字八法 | EightStrokes Calligraphy" description="永字八法 (EightStrokes) — 每日一练，笔尖修禅。指尖落笔即得评分，一键分享书法佳作。" />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main class="yong-page">
			<div class="hero-container">
				<div class="hero-content">
					<div class="app-tag">🎉 App Store 新鲜上架 · Now Available</div>
					<h1>永字八法 / EightStrokes</h1>
					<p class="subtitle">每日一练，笔尖修禅。随时随地用指尖开启你的书法修行。</p>
					<p class="tagline">Practice daily, find zen in every stroke. Start your calligraphy journey anytime, anywhere with just your fingertip.</p>
					
					<div class="cta-group">
						<a href="https://apps.apple.com/ca/app/8strokes/id6774579880" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary"> App Store 下载 / Download</a>
						<a href="#features" class="btn btn-secondary">探索核心特色 / Explore Features</a>
					</div>
					<p class="coming-soon">🚀 现已支持 iPad · <strong>iPhone 版本、更多字帖与更多平台兼容即将到来</strong><br /><span class="en-sub">Now on iPad · iPhone, more copybooks & broader device support coming soon</span></p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="hero-preview">
					<img src="/images/yong-preview.png" alt="永字八法 iPad 样机预览" class="framed-mockup" />
				</div>
			</div>

			<section class="demo-section">
				<h2>极速手感与智能反馈 / Fluid Touch & Smart Feedback</h2>
				<p class="demo-subtitle">在 iPad 屏幕上，用最简单的动作，体验极低延迟的矢量书法演算。<br /><span class="en-sub">Experience ultra-low-latency vector calligraphy rendering on your iPad with the simplest gestures.</span></p>
				
				<div class="demo-grid">
					<div class="demo-card">
						<div class="video-container">
							<video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="demo-video">
								<source src="/videos/yong-demo-2.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
								Your browser does not support the video tag.
							</video>
						</div>
						<div class="demo-info">
							<h4>指尖即墨 · 实时渲染 / Real-time Ink Rendering</h4>
							<p>依托低延迟渲染引擎，无缝捕捉压感与轨迹，完美呈现水墨晕染与笔锋顿挫。</p>
							<small>Powered by a low-latency rendering engine that captures pressure and trajectory to produce authentic ink wash effects and brush dynamics.</small>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="demo-card">
						<div class="video-container">
							<video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="demo-video demo-video-zoom">
								<source src="/videos/yong-demo-1.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
								Your browser does not support the video tag.
							</video>
						</div>
						<div class="demo-info">
							<h4>端侧智能评测打分 / On-Device Smart Scoring</h4>
							<p>规则与 ML 引擎多维度精准考量笔顺、结构与平滑度，给出即时、细致的书写评分反馈。</p>
							<small>A hybrid rule-based and ML engine evaluates stroke order, structure, and smoothness to provide instant, detailed scoring feedback.</small>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section id="features" class="features-section">
				<h2>核心特色 / Core Features</h2>
				<div class="features-grid">
					<div class="feature-card">
						<div class="feature-icon">✨</div>
						<h3>指尖即墨 / Fingertip Ink</h3>
						<p>无需纸墨，指尖即笔。屏幕上会呈现如宣纸般晕染浸润的优美笔迹，完美还原汉字横折撇捺的骨骼与神韵。</p>
						<small>No ink or paper needed — draw naturally with your finger or stylus. The screen renders beautiful ink strokes that mimic the diffusion of brush on rice paper, faithfully reproducing the structure and spirit of each character.</small>
					</div>

					<div class="feature-card">
						<div class="feature-icon">📅</div>
						<h3>每日一练 / Daily Habit</h3>
						<p>每天一分钟的静心练习，经典的“永”字八笔成型。在忙碌的日常中寻得片刻宁静，磨练专注力与写字法度。</p>
						<small>One minute a day of mindful practice with the legendary "Yong" (永) character — the one character whose eight strokes encompass every fundamental brush technique. Find a moment of calm in your busy day and sharpen your focus.</small>
					</div>

					<div class="feature-card">
						<div class="feature-icon">🤖</div>
						<h3>智能评分 / On-Device Grading</h3>
						<p>应用内置智能评分引擎，从笔顺、间架平衡度、笔画平滑度等多个维度为您实时打分，您的每一次进步都清晰可见。</p>
						<small>Built-in smart scoring engine rates your writing in real time across multiple dimensions — stroke order, structural balance, and smoothness — so every improvement is visible at a glance.</small>
					</div>

					<div class="feature-card">
						<div class="feature-icon">✉️</div>
						<h3>雅致分享 / Elegant Sharing</h3>
						<p>对自己的高分作品感到骄傲？一键生成古典、精美的书法打分卡片，轻松分享到朋友圈或以笔会友。</p>
						<small>Proud of a high score? Generate an elegant, minimalist scorecard in one tap and share it with friends — challenge each other and bond through the art of calligraphy.</small>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section id="blessing" class="blessing-section">
				<h2>祝福卡片 · 同框分享 / Blessing Cards & Shareable Moments</h2>
				<p class="blessing-subtitle">把一笔一画的心意，写进一张可分享的祝福卡。挥毫落墨，随手相赠。<br /><span class="en-sub">Turn every stroke into a heartfelt blessing card you can share. Write elegantly and gift effortlessly.</span></p>

				<div class="blessing-grid">
					<figure class="blessing-card-item">
						<img src="/images/04_blessing_card_ipad.png" alt="永字八法 祝福卡片 iPad 样机预览 / EightStrokes Blessing Card on iPad" loading="lazy" />
						<figcaption>
							<h4>🧧 祝福卡片 / Blessing Card</h4>
							<p>挥毫写下祝福，一键生成古典雅致的祝福卡片，把指尖的墨香送给最在意的人。</p>
							<small>Write a blessing by hand and generate an elegant, classical card in one tap — send the scent of ink to the people who matter most.</small>
						</figcaption>
					</figure>

					<figure class="blessing-card-item">
						<img src="/images/05_replay_score_card_ipad.png" alt="永字八法 笔迹回放评分卡 iPad 样机预览 / EightStrokes Replay Scorecard on iPad" loading="lazy" />
						<figcaption>
							<h4>🎞️ 回放评分卡 / Replay Scorecard</h4>
							<p>逐笔回放你的书写过程，搭配多维度评分卡，随时复盘每一次落笔与进步。</p>
							<small>Replay your writing stroke by stroke alongside a multi-dimensional scorecard — review every stroke and watch yourself improve.</small>
						</figcaption>
					</figure>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section id="support" class="support-section">
				<div class="section-container">
					<h2>技术支持与反馈 / Support & Feedback</h2>
					<p>在使用 <strong>永字八法 (EightStrokes)</strong> 的过程中，如果您有任何疑问、发现 Bug、或者有任何功能性的建议，欢迎通过以下渠道与我们取得联系：</p>
					<p class="english-law">If you have any questions, find a bug, or have feature suggestions while using <strong>EightStrokes</strong>, please reach out through the channels below:</p>
					
					<div class="contact-methods">
						<div class="contact-card">
							<h4>✉️ 电子邮件 / Email</h4>
							<p><a href="mailto:victor@goldenarc.digital">victor@goldenarc.digital</a></p>
							<small>我们通常会在 24 小时内回复您的问题。<br />We typically respond within 24 hours.</small>
						</div>
						
						<div class="contact-card">
							<h4>🔒 源码与反馈 / Repository & Feedback</h4>
							<p>私有代码仓库 / Private Repository</p>
							<small>本项目代码仓目前为私有，暂不支持公开提交 Issue。欢迎通过电子邮件与我们进行交流。<br />The repository is currently private. Technical feedback and ideas are welcome via email.</small>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section id="privacy" class="privacy-section">
				<div class="section-container">
					<h2>隐私政策 / Privacy Policy</h2>
					<p class="update-date">最后更新日期：2026年5月29日 · Last updated: May 29, 2026</p>
					
					<div class="privacy-content">
						<h3>1. 个人数据收集说明 / No Personal Data Collection</h3>
						<p><strong>永字八法 (EightStrokes)</strong> 极其尊重您的个人隐私。我们<strong>不会收集、存储、分享或上传</strong>您的任何个人信息、手写笔迹数据、打分结果或设备标识符。</p>
						<p class="english-law">We do not collect, store, share, or upload any of your personal information, drawing strokes, scorecards, or device identifiers.</p>

						<h3>2. 端侧处理保证 / 100% On-Device Processing</h3>
						<p>应用内所有的轨迹演算、图形网格生成以及智能评分等级计算，均<strong>完全在您的本地设备上进行（On-Device Processing）</strong>。评分模型（包括规则引擎与 CoreML 技术）全部离线运行，无需联网，保证您的书写修行绝对私密安全。</p>
						<p class="english-law">All calculations, brush tessellation, and stroke evaluation are computed entirely offline and locally on your device.</p>

						<h3>3. 第三方SDK与广告 / No Third-party SDKs or Ads</h3>
						<p>本应用<strong>不包含任何第三方广告 SDK 或数据分析追踪工具</strong>，我们致力于为您提供纯净无干扰的书写修身空间。</p>
						<p class="english-law">The application does not integrate any advertising SDKs or tracking tools.</p>

						<h3>4. 隐私政策的更新 / Updates</h3>
						<p>我们可能会不时更新本隐私政策。若有任何重大更改，我们将通过应用内公告或此网页及时告知您。</p>
						<p class="english-law">We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any material changes will be communicated via in-app announcements or on this page.</p>

						<h3>5. 联系我们 / Contact Us</h3>
						<p>如果您对我们的隐私政策有任何问题，欢迎随时发信联络我们：<a href="mailto:victor@goldenarc.digital">victor@goldenarc.digital</a>。</p>
						<p class="english-law">If you have any questions about our privacy policy, feel free to contact us at <a href="mailto:victor@goldenarc.digital">victor@goldenarc.digital</a>.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.yong-page {
		width: min(1140px, 100%);
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 3rem 1.25rem;
		font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
		color: #2c2927;
	}

	/* Hero Section */
	.hero-container {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
		gap: 3.5rem;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 2rem 0 4rem 0;
	}

	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.hero-container {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2.5rem;
			text-align: center;
		}
		
		.cta-group {
			justify-content: center;
		}
	}

	.app-tag {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.35rem 0.85rem;
		background: rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.1);
		color: #8b7355;
		border-radius: 99px;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
	}

	.hero-content h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		line-height: 1.15;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
		margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
		color: #1a1716;
	}

	.subtitle {
		font-size: 1.35rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		line-height: 1.5;
		color: #5c5652;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.tagline {
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
		color: #8b837e;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}

	.cta-group {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.coming-soon {
		margin-top: 1.25rem;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
		color: #8b7355;
	}

	.coming-soon strong {
		color: #735f46;
	}

	.coming-soon .en-sub {
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: #9c938e;
	}

	.btn {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.85rem 1.6rem;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		border-radius: 99px;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
	}

	.btn:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}

	.btn-primary {
		background: #8b7355;
		color: #ffffff;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.25);
	}

	.btn-primary:hover {
		background: #735f46;
		box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.35);
	}

	.btn-secondary {
		background: rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.06);
		color: #8b7355;
		border: 1px solid rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.2);
	}

	.btn-secondary:hover {
		background: rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.12);
	}

	.framed-mockup {
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 440px;
		height: auto;
		border-radius: 24px;
		box-shadow: 0 20px 45px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
		display: block;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	/* Demo Videos Section */
	.demo-section {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.15);
	}

	.demo-section h2 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		color: #1a1716;
	}

	.demo-subtitle {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: #8b837e;
		margin-bottom: 3.5rem !important;
	}

	.demo-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 2.5rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.demo-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2rem;
		}
	}

	.demo-card {
		background: #fafaf7;
		border: 1px solid rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.1);
		border-radius: 24px;
		overflow: hidden;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);
		transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
	}

	.demo-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-4px);
		box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.08);
	}

	.video-container {
		width: 100%;
		aspect-ratio: 16 / 12;
		overflow: hidden;
		background: #000;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.1);
	}

	.demo-video {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
		transition: transform 0.3s ease;
	}

	.demo-video-zoom {
		object-position: center bottom;
		transform: scale(1.38);
		transform-origin: center bottom;
	}

	/* Subtle micro-animation to scale up the zoom slightly on hover */
	.demo-card:hover .demo-video-zoom {
		transform: scale(1.45);
	}

	.demo-info {
		padding: 1.75rem;
	}

	.demo-info h4 {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		color: #1a1716;
	}

	.demo-info p {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: #5c5652;
		margin: 0;
	}

	/* Features Section */
	.features-section {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.15);
	}

	.features-section h2 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
		color: #1a1716;
	}

	.features-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.feature-card {
		padding: 2.25rem 1.75rem;
		background: #fafaf7;
		border: 1px solid rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.1);
		border-radius: 20px;
		transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
	}

	.feature-card:hover {
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.06);
		border-color: rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.25);
	}

	.feature-icon {
		font-size: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
	}

	.feature-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		color: #1a1716;
	}

	.feature-card p {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: #5c5652;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.feature-card small {
		display: block;
		font-size: 0.82rem;
		line-height: 1.4;
		color: #9c938e;
	}

	/* Blessing Cards Section */
	.blessing-section {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.15);
	}

	.blessing-section h2 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		color: #1a1716;
	}

	.blessing-subtitle {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: #8b837e;
		margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
	}

	.blessing-subtitle .en-sub {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	.blessing-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 2.5rem;
		align-items: start;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.blessing-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2.5rem;
		}
	}

	.blessing-card-item {
		margin: 0;
	}

	.blessing-card-item img {
		width: 100%;
		height: auto;
		border-radius: 20px;
		box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
		display: block;
	}

	.blessing-card-item figcaption {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
	}

	.blessing-card-item h4 {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		color: #1a1716;
	}

	.blessing-card-item p {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: #5c5652;
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
	}

	.blessing-card-item small {
		display: block;
		font-size: 0.82rem;
		line-height: 1.4;
		color: #9c938e;
	}

	/* Support & Privacy Common */
	.support-section, .privacy-section {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.15);
	}

	.section-container {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.section-container h2 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		color: #1a1716;
	}

	.section-container p {
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		line-height: 1.65;
		color: #5c5652;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	/* Support Grid */
	.contact-methods {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 600px) {
		.contact-methods {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 1.5rem;
		}
	}

	.contact-card {
		padding: 1.75rem;
		background: #ffffff;
		border: 1px solid rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.15);
		border-radius: 16px;
	}

	.contact-card h4 {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		color: #1a1716;
	}

	.contact-card p {
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.contact-card p a {
		color: #8b7355;
		text-decoration: underline;
	}

	.contact-card small {
		display: block;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: #8b837e;
	}

	/* Privacy Style */
	.update-date {
		font-size: 0.9rem !important;
		color: #8b837e !important;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem !important;
	}

	.privacy-content {
		background: #fafaf7;
